<h3 id="how-to-uninstall-">How to uninstall ?</h3>
<p>Delete the Assembly-CSharp.dll file from Manager folder, then go on steam, Seum game -&gt; properties -&gt; local files -&gt; Verify integrity of game files...  </p>

